### Comparison: Which Loader to Use
```
Option A: Raw msfvenom exe
  → Fastest, no compilation
  → Gets caught by any AV immediately
  → Use only if Defender is already disabled

Option B: Byte array C# loader
  → Quick to set up, one msfvenom + one compile
  → Evades signature-based AV (unique hash per compile)
  → May get caught by heuristic AV (raw shellcode bytes visible in binary)

Option C: IPv4 formatter C# loader
  → Extra step (python converter) but more evasive
  → Shellcode stored as IP address strings, not raw bytes
  → Evades both signature and basic heuristic analysis
  → Use when Option B still gets flagged
```

