### Why These Loaders Evade AV
```
Raw msfvenom exe  → known signature → Defender flags instantly
Byte array loader → custom compile  → unique hash, no known signature
IPv4 loader       → shellcode as IP strings → evades signature + heuristic

Both methods:
  → VirtualAlloc + CreateThread is generic Win32 API usage (not flagged)
  → Each compilation produces a different binary hash
  → Shellcode is embedded data, not a known malware pattern
```
